      <h1>Understanding Film Funding Opportunities in Switzerland</h1>
      <p class="lead">Explore film funding opportunities in Switzerland. Learn how Viven helps you navigate co-production incentives and financial support.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>December 15, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 18, 2025</span></p>
    </div>
